      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>BORISOFF--Ida. The partners, counsel, associates and staff of the firm of Paul, Weiss, Rifkind, Wharton &amp; Garrison LLP express profound sorrow at the death on May 19 of Ida Borisoff, beloved mother of our friend and partner, Richard S. Borisoff. We express our deepest sympathies to Richard and to all other members of the family.</p>
      </block>
